message: "If you use this environment or its results, please cite it as below."
title: "no-start-env"
abstract: >-
  An agentic RL environment and eval: a simulated vehicle with electrical
  no-start and charging faults that an LLM agent diagnoses and repairs using
  realistic tools, scored by a cheat-resistant grader. Built on Inspect
  (inspect-ai).
